  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"hfxiJx8m\">反正我用，而且我之前偶然看见我导师还在用呢！</p><h3>给你推荐这个文献翻译工具，简直是文献翻译、润色、修改集于一体的全能神器！</h3><p data-pid=\"T6jRZvQ_\">有用的话记得收藏哦，下次用的时候找不到了！</p><h3>文献翻译工具：<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=643614802&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=Dochero.AI&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">Dochero.AI<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span></h3><p data-pid=\"059ZC6D8\">这个翻译神器能很好地理解文化背景，根据语意来翻译，比<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=643614802&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=DeepL&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">DeepL<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>强太多啦!</p><p data-pid=\"cRb7mDm_\">可以选择各种语言模式和风格，支持中文、英文、日语、德语等多种语言，还可以设定学术、商务、专业、亲切等语言风格。</p><p data-pid=\"cMRUvFHG\">更贴心的是，根据上下文语境进行分析，轻松帮你解决翻译不准确、结构不流畅的问题！</p><p data-pid=\"rwzk-Rvt\">需要提醒的是，<b>每天可以免费使用39次，不过也不用担心，换个浏览器还可以用。</b></p><h3>使用方法:</h3><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee0bf77e69b128a407cc0ba4668e0383_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"601\" data-rawheight=\"784\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee0bf77e69b128a407cc0ba4668e0383\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"601\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ee0bf77e69b128a407cc0ba4668e0383_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='601' height='784'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"601\" data-rawheight=\"784\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee0bf77e69b128a407cc0ba4668e0383\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"601\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ee0bf77e69b128a407cc0ba4668e0383_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee0bf77e69b128a407cc0ba4668e0383_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7df5dc89eeea967de094d06685f57290_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"601\" data-rawheight=\"809\" data-original-token=\"v2-7df5dc89eeea967de094d06685f57290\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"601\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-7df5dc89eeea967de094d06685f57290_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='601' height='809'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"601\" data-rawheight=\"809\" data-original-token=\"v2-7df5dc89eeea967de094d06685f57290\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"601\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-7df5dc89eeea967de094d06685f57290_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7df5dc89eeea967de094d06685f57290_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6b6b14c4d8b93f9e38512b970d5eaa56_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"614\" data-rawheight=\"803\" data-original-token=\"v2-6b6b14c4d8b93f9e38512b970d5eaa56\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"614\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-6b6b14c4d8b93f9e38512b970d5eaa56_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='614' height='803'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"614\" data-rawheight=\"803\" data-original-token=\"v2-6b6b14c4d8b93f9e38512b970d5eaa56\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"614\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-6b6b14c4d8b93f9e38512b970d5eaa56_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6b6b14c4d8b93f9e38512b970d5eaa56_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"MV8bqtPa\">无论是在阅读英文文献时感到一脸懵，还是在润色修改论文时无从下手，都能帮你一键搞定！</p><p data-pid=\"wnIih9yF\">这是一个浏览器插件，如果你不会下载可以来找我领操作方法！</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><h3>再给大家分享几个超级好用的文献阅读工具：</h3><h3>1.Chatdoc：</h3><p data-pid=\"p0wsx5p1\">文献<span class=\"nolink\">阅读工具，操作简单，一键上传，快速上手，可以对文献进行智能分析，</span>帮你提炼文献主要内容，通过提问的方式快速检索全文，然后再给出回答，节省时间很方便快捷。</p><p data-pid=\"dR8jYXQZ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.chatdoc.com/\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">chatdoc.com/</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0ef405d17ae66cd0459fab6950c931c0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1840\" data-rawheight=\"844\" data-original-token=\"v2-0ef405d17ae66cd0459fab6950c931c0\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1840\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0ef405d17ae66cd0459fab6950c931c0_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1840' height='844'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1840\" data-rawheight=\"844\" data-original-token=\"v2-0ef405d17ae66cd0459fab6950c931c0\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1840\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0ef405d17ae66cd0459fab6950c931c0_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0ef405d17ae66cd0459fab6950c931c0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><h3>2.<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=643614802&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=Docalysis&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">Docalysis<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span><span class=\"nolink\">：</span></h3><p data-pid=\"sp5uHFqY\">通过划线帮你总结文献段落大意，也支持提问问答，基于提交的文献帮你了解文献的具体内容。</p><p data-pid=\"lKkGlOs0\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//docalysis.com/\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">docalysis.com/</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d0e440a8d2632125dbf680707b89935c_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" dat