cy.com/</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-368880efd9fea95e3bbfc7dbf8123285_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1797\" data-rawheight=\"906\" data-original-token=\"v2-368880efd9fea95e3bbfc7dbf8123285\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1797\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-368880efd9fea95e3bbfc7dbf8123285_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1797' height='906'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1797\" data-rawheight=\"906\" data-original-token=\"v2-368880efd9fea95e3bbfc7dbf8123285\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1797\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-368880efd9fea95e3bbfc7dbf8123285_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-368880efd9fea95e3bbfc7dbf8123285_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"TKSVU3Bj\">以上就是关于阅读文献的工具分享，如果你还不知道如何检索和下载文献，可以看看我这几篇高赞回答：</p><div class=\"RichText-LinkCardContainer\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/answer/3188130346\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-text=\"怎样查全一个方向的文献？导师总问「你查全了吗」？\" class=\"LinkCard new css-jqz2mj\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5f37ce09cb0df9d0c68f1d45fe4106ad_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1627\" data-image-height=\"744\"><span class=\"LinkCard-image LinkCard-image--default\"></span><span class=\"LinkCard-contents\"><span class=\"LinkCard-title loading\" data-text=\"true\"></span><span class=\"LinkCard-desc loading\"></span></span></a></div><div class=\"RichText-LinkCardContainer\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/answer/3299519941\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-text=\"研究生如何获取自己研究领域最新的英文文献？\" class=\"LinkCard new css-jqz2mj\" data-image=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2